4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp emphasizes risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Courses are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop